# Minime Alpine world (RK3326) — board-specific package set.
#
# RK3326 / PX30 ships Mali Bifrost G31 (Rockchip).  Like H700, the Mali
# driver pair (libmali / mali_kbase) is intentionally absent in V1; we
# use Mesa Panfrost with DRM/GBM/KMS for GLES.  See the same caveat in
# configs/world-h700 about the G31's GLES performance.
#
# Board-specific deltas:
#   - Some RK3326 handhelds ship with USB Wi-Fi / Bluetooth dongles
#     (RTL8811AU, ESP-8089) instead of the internal SDIO module.  The
#     matching firmware fragments are copied to /lib/firmware by
#     minime-overlay's post-install, mirroring Buildroot's post-build.sh.

# Inherit world-common behavior is provided by build.sh, which concatenates
# world-common and world-<board> at install time.  This file currently
# contributes no extra packages, but is preserved so the board delta
# remains explicit and version-controllable.
